    "date": "2019-11-13T16:23:45Z",
    "text": "Patient Access to ESRD New Innovative Devices Act\n\nThis bill requires the Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services (CMS) to establish a process to provide a certain payment adjustment under the Medicare end-stage renal disease (ESRD) prospective payment system. Specifically, the CMS must establish a process to provide for a temporary add-on payment adjustment for new medical devices used to diagnose, treat, or manage ESRD."
